{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_ceylon_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_ceylon_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"真心的礼物","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"圣诞节前夕，锡兰在商业街碰到了自己的同学琳兹。锡兰盛情邀请对方陪自己挑选礼物，却丝毫没有注意到琳兹神色中的尴尬。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_ceylon_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["商店广播","锡兰","琳兹","店员","黑","赫尔曼"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_bg_bg_school.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_distressed_loop.mp3","volume":"0.3","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"text","text":"“几个月前我刚进入大学的时候，寄了一张国立大学图书馆的明信片给你。”","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"“那时我仰望着四周向穹顶延伸的书架，听着过道上同学们的脚步声在庞大的建筑内回响，我是多么兴奋啊。”","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"“我觉得这里的知识是无穷的，其中一定有我要的答案——能治好你的方法。”","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"“但现在站在同样的地方，我总是感到一阵眩晕，走向书架的每一步也变得更加艰难。”","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"“我开始害怕图书馆、实验室和教室，畏惧像过去一样拼命努力；我在每一行看不懂的文字面前感到疲倦无比。”","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"“我忍不住想，要是我的时间不够学习所有我想要的知识呢？”","id":13},{"type":"text","text":"“......要是我就像抽干汐斯塔的海一样，穷尽了这里的知识，却仍然得不到那个答案呢？”","id":14},{"type":"text","text":"“我该怎么办？”","id":15},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper2","volume":"1","id":16},{"type":"text","text":"——一张作废的信笺，被折成三折塞在了垃圾桶底部。","id":17},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":18},{"type":"dialog","id":19},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","fadetime":"3","volume":"0.4","id":21,"musicid":1},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_bg_21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":22},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"商店广播","text":"“......圣诞节特款萨米风味肉桂热饮，老少咸宜，家庭套餐买二送一，可抽取圣诞信使的惊喜玩具......”","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"商店广播","text":"“......冰原信使系列新款上架，给您家的温暖......”","id":25},{"type":"dialog","id":26},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":27},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"原来圣诞促销活动已经开始了呀......每年这个时候商业区都会热闹起来。","id":29,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"这家“杰奎琳小姐”茶室，自从黑回去之后我好像就没来过了。对不起哦，杰奎琳小姐，你们的点心架分量太足了，我一个人吃不完。","id":31,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"萝茜百货大楼应该就在转角，不过黑已经陪我去逛过很多次了，大概没有什么可以让她感到惊喜的礼物吧。","id":33,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"那边应该可以直接雇佣国际信使。虽说队伍比别的地方长太多了，但是在商店街买好贺卡之后可以直接跟信一起寄出去。","id":35,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"嗯，寄给父亲的贺卡就不需要写字了吧。","id":36,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":37},{"type":"character","id":38},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_032","fadetime":"1","id":39},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":40},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","id":41},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-250","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":42},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"250","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":43},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":44},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"啊，琳兹！中午好！","id":47,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":48},{"type":"jump","name":"right","xpos":"10","power":"5","times":"1","fadetime":"0.4","block":"true","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"欸、欸？中午好，锡兰，没想到会在这里遇见你......","id":50,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"（小声）怎么是她啊，麻烦......","id":51,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"怎么了？","id":53,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"不，我没说什么......只是没想到锡兰你居然记得我的名字。","id":55,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"咦，我看起来记忆力有那么不好吗？我记得刚开学的时候，就是你教会我怎么区分维多利亚铸币的。","id":57,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"除了走廊上的老式投币售货机和公用电话机，我从没见过还有什么地方用得上它们。","id":58,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"自动售货机接受的是老式铸币，但是我投进去的是新式铸币，所以它卡住了，还是靠你拍了半天才好。","id":59,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"还有第一次“星期四诗与茶会”的时候，也是你事先提醒了我不要念威廉姆斯的诗，因为他太有名了。","id":60,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"哎，文学毕竟不是我的兴趣方向嘛！","id":62,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"那你估计也还记得上次野外考察的时候，你一个人的报告太详尽，导致全组其他人贡献度大大降低，获得的分数也很难看。","id":64,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"嗯？","id":66,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"没什么，我是说，我也不是真的在怀疑你的记忆力。","id":68,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"你也是来逛街的吗？","id":69,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"对呀，圣诞节要到了，该准备一些礼物了。","id":71,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"正好，琳兹你是本地人，请你陪我逛逛可以吗？","id":73,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"虽说我也来维多利亚几年了，但平时只会去大型百货商店，对那些藏在街巷中的精品店还是不太了解。","id":74,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"呃，我......","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"抱歉，你有别的事情要忙？","id":78,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"对了，确实圣诞节假期前还有几篇阶段性报告要写，你要是没有心思逛街我也可以理解。","id":79,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"不不，那些报告我已经完成一半了。","id":81,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"拜托，会提前做功课的人也不是只有你一个。","id":82,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"可是一旦做起实验来，时间永远是不够的嘛。","id":84,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"唉......","id":86,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"你要买什么样的礼物？既然你那么不想浪费时间，我们就动作快点。","id":87,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"随便看看也没关系，我要准备的礼物有很多件呢。偶然看到中意的就买下来，这样才算是逛街嘛。","id":89,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"啊？......呃，没想到你也会有随便逛逛的闲心。","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"只是今天觉得自己特别需要休息。正好，圣诞节也是个不错的借口。","id":93,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"......你可真擅长让人没心情过节。","id":95,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"算了，这边的台阶下去，巷子里有一家手工巧克力店，我们先去看看吧。","id":96,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"这家有二十几种不重样的礼盒，可以买来送给不同的人。这样你应该能快点买完所有礼物吧。","id":97,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialog","id":98},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":99},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":100},{"type":"character","id":101},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/41/Avg_bg_21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d.png","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","id":102},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":103},{"type":"backgroundtween","xFrom":"0","yFrom":"10","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"2.5","block":"false","id":104},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":105},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","id":106},{"type":"jump","name":"left","xpos":"0","power":"3","times":"5","fadetime":"4","block":"false","id":107},{"type":"jump","name":"right","xpos":"0","power":"3","times":"5","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":108},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":109},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"锡兰，你有在听我说话吗？你又在想什么啊？","id":111,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"啊，抱歉......","id":113,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"你今天看起来可真奇怪。","id":115,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","id":116},{"type":"dialog","id":117},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":118},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"店员","text":"两位女士，要尝尝我们这边的圣诞新款吗？店内有不同样式的礼盒装售卖哦。","id":120},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"谢谢，我们正好要看巧克力，请多多介绍。","id":122,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"嗯......这个试吃的巧克力味道不错！请问这是哪一款？","id":124,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"店员","text":"覆盆子碎配白巧克力，现在有雪景主题的圣诞礼盒款哦。","id":126},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"琳兹你看！包装感觉和薇薇安的发色很搭呢，就送这个给她吧。","id":128,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"嗯......嗯？","id":130,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"——你刚刚说要给薇薇安买礼物？","id":131,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"是哦，你是觉得巧克力太普通了吗？","id":133,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"不是，我是想，可是你们前两天还吵了一架欸。","id":135,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"唔，你指的是前两天我们在理论课上讨论狄安娜教授核心理念的事？那个我昨天已经向她道歉了呀。","id":137,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"《源石、分离机与摇撼的大地》这本小册子里面，狄安娜教授对源石的应用实验已经转向民用范畴，但是之前我没来得及读到。","id":138,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"不，也不仅是前两天......每次小组合作开会的时候你们都在吵架吧？","id":140,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"你们就像仇家一样。","id":141,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"有吗？可是我觉得自己在她的帮助下获得了很多新知识哦，感激她都来不及。","id":143,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"个人的认知总是非常有限的，要接近真知，就必须要去找和自己想法不同的人，多多进行这样的交流。","id":145,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"你啊......","id":147,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我会离开家乡来到维多利亚学习，这应该是主要原因吧。","id":149,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"在汐斯塔，人人都说感染者是无法被治愈的，所以我决定离开汐斯塔，看看其他地域、其他时代的人们会不会有不一样的回答。","id":151,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"古老的维多利亚，会不会比年轻的汐斯塔懂得更多呢？","id":152,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"大概会吧......","id":154,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"——欸，等等，感染者？锡兰你是想治疗感染者？","id":156,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"嗯，你是不是觉得这个想法不太......","id":158,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"难怪你会莫名其妙地申请选修药学院的课程，还直接把陈述书投到了学院院长的信箱里，闹出了不小的动静。","id":160,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"不过国立大学的药学院可是出了名的严格，就算他们接受一个旁听生，大概也不会给你任何资质证明吧。","id":161,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"给不给资质证明倒是没关系，只是我......","id":163,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",10]},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":164},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"——啊，店员小姐，您好，请帮我挑两盒礼盒装巧克力一起结账吧，谢谢。","id":166,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",0]},{"type":"character","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"店员","text":"好的，请来这边。","id":168},{"type":"dialog","id":169},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":170},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":171},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":172},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":173},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_032","block":"true","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"唉，结果完全没找到机会把她赶走，差点还听她讲下去了。","id":175,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"要不我现在自己溜走吧。再这么一直陪着她，我今天来商业街要做的事情就做不成了。","id":176,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialog","id":177},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":178},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":179},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我买好了，接下来我们去哪里？","id":181,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"......你回来得可真及时。","id":183,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"对了，因为琳兹你今天在场，所以今天我不会买你的圣诞礼物，只会买其他朋友的礼物。","id":185,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"呃，还有我的圣诞礼物？我们的关系有那么......","id":187,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"（小声）唉，你要是知道我做了什么，肯定就不会觉得我是你的朋友了。","id":188,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"毕竟当着你的面买的话，就不算惊喜了嘛。","id":190,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":191},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"咳......咳咳！啊，是呢，是这样的。","id":193,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"好啦，拜托你领路啦，我们去下一家看看吧。","id":195,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":196},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":197},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":198},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":199},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","fadetime":"0.5","id":200},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":201},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"嗯......虽然最重要的一件礼物还没有挑好，不过今天选不到也没关系。毕竟“最重要”的东西，不多花点心思可不行。","id":203,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"除此之外要买的就只剩下一张贺卡了。买完之后去那边办理一下国际信使雇佣服务，今天的任务就算结束了。","id":204,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"又要寄国际邮件？你的家书也太频繁了吧......雇佣费可不便宜。而且，你不是马上就要回家了吗？","id":206,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我还要过好多天才能到家呢。再说，这张贺卡，寄回去比当面递交好。","id":208,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"说起来，琳兹你自己还什么都没买，是不是我耽误你的计划了？你要是有什么想去逛逛的店铺，也可以带着我一起去嘛。","id":210,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"天都快黑了，再晚一点店铺可都要关门了。","id":211,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"......唉，好吧，我认命了。","id":213,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"我想去那边的家居用品店看看，你要是没有兴趣的话不用等我。","id":214,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"家居用品吗？我很有兴趣！","id":216,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"（小声）......我还是比较希望你没有兴趣。","id":218,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialog","id":219},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":220},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":221},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":222},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_032","fadetime":"0.5","id":223},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":224},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-300","fadetime":"2.5","block":"false","id":225},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":226},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_slbellbtl","id":227},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"您好，我是琳兹，昨天在你们门店下过预购单，这是提货码。","id":229,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"啊对了，麻烦直接包装好可以吗？是送人的礼物。","id":230,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_032","focus":"3","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"店员","text":"没问题。核验完毕，这是您预订的商品。需要系上圣诞卡片吗？","id":232,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_032","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"不，不用了，谢谢。","id":234,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","id":235},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"你买了什么？","id":237,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"全自动茶壶，按照说明书放入定量的水和茶包，它就会帮你控制水温，保证你泡出来的红茶口感。","id":239,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我听说过！唔，不知道是用怎样的源石施术单元实现的呢......能不能拆开看看说明书......","id":241,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"咳，这个你拿着继续研究吧，不用还给我了。","id":243,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"咦？这不是你送人的礼物吗？","id":245,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"......呃。","id":247,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"它是送给你的。","id":249,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialog","id":250},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","id":251},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":252},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$holiday_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_holiday_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"3","id":253,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","id":254},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":255},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"你想笑就笑吧。我也没想到这么不巧。","id":257,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"噗。","id":259,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"之后同学们一起喝下午茶的时候，如果你愿意用这个茶壶而不是自己手工沏茶，我会非常高兴的......其他人估计也会很高兴。","id":261,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"谢谢你。","id":263,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"可是现在离圣诞节还有一个月，离我们放假也还有两周欸。","id":264,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"（深呼吸）","id":266,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"这不是圣诞礼物，是我向你表示歉意的礼物。","id":267,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"欸？","id":269,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"......请不要那么茫然地看着我，你这样会让我更加没勇气认错的。","id":271,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"对不起，我以前一直不敢跟你讲话。","id":272,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"呃，其实不仅是我，大家都有点害怕你。","id":273,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"嗯？为什么会害怕我啊......因为我想治疗感染者？","id":275,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":276},{"type":"jump","name":"right","xpos":"0","power":"6","times":"2","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"不是，完全不是！我之前都没听说过这件事！我只是觉得你实在太努力了！","id":278,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"一个来自炎热城市的人能在冬季的早上六点爬出被窝去图书馆占座，到底是多可怕的自律能力啊！","id":279,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"早上十点去吃早午餐的时候碰到你捧着书在回廊上踱步，感觉你打招呼的眼神都像是在说“怎么这个时间才起床”一样。","id":280,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"总之，锡兰你就像冷冰冰的镜子一样，我走过的时候就会看到自己懒惰散漫的样子。","id":281,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我有那么冷冰冰的吗？","id":283,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"别、别误会，我是在夸你。","id":285,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"——对了，我想冒昧地问一个问题可以吗？","id":286,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"你有关系很好的感染者朋友吗？","id":287,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"哎？！","id":289,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"......嗯，有哦。她是我最重要的人。","id":291,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"她现在还好吗？","id":293,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"情况一直很稳定。没有什么东西能打倒她，矿石病也不能。","id":295,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"那就好。","id":297,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"......还有，她不在维多利亚，所以这里的管理条例对她不生效，如果你想对她......","id":299,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"不不，我没有恶意，也不是什么猎奇的心态。","id":301,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"我们可是源石研究者欸，也许哪天因为实验事故、观测时的突发状况，甚至因为自己主动的意愿，我们都可能感染矿石病。","id":302,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"我们知道它是什么，或者至少比大多数人更接近于知道。","id":303,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"......谢谢你，琳兹。","id":305,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"唉，也许应该是我来说感谢吧。","id":307,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"就像你的理想是治疗感染者一样......来国立大学读书，选择了源石研究这个专业的人，就算是我，也有自己小小的理想。","id":308,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"我虽然知道学者的理想就意味着实现前人未能达成的事情，意味着要把一条路走到头，然后自己开辟出新的道路......但我远没有做好准备。","id":309,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"前人未能达成的事情......","id":311,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"——还好有你这样的榜样在身边。","id":313,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"是这样吗？我......有能力成为这样的人吗？","id":315,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",10]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"我真的是在夸你呀，别露出那样的表情。","id":317,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"不，别在意。我刚刚是想起了别的事情......想通了一些事情。","id":319,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"对了，我要把这件礼物还给你。之前只是我们还不熟悉而已，这有什么可道歉的？","id":321,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"啊......那个，最重要的事情我还没说呢......","id":323,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"其实我要道歉的是，因为不敢跟你说话，所以我也没有告诉你，之前天灾现场采集的源石样本出现了一些稀有反应。","id":324,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"15","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":325},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"1","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"什么！","id":327,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","focus":"2","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"我对自己的实验方法和观测结果都没有什么信心，总觉得只是我自己少见多怪......","id":329,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"......要是锡兰你看了之后说这不是什么新发现，我该有多丢脸呀！","id":330,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"所以，即使我知道你应该是对这些进展最有兴趣的人，我也没敢分享——","id":331,"figure":"avg_npc_032"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","id":332},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.8","id":333},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"250","fadetime":"1.7","block":"false","id":334},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.8","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","id":335},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"-1","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"3","vibrato":"5","randomness":"90","block":"false","id":336},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":337},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"20","fadetime":"0.8","block":"false","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我们快跑起来！下一班回学校的车还有三分钟到站！","id":339,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","id":340},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"170","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":341},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":342},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"170","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"只要赶在实验室关门之前溜进去，我们就可以在里面待一晚上！","id":344,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",1]},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":345},{"type":"character","name":"avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_032","id":346},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"170","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":347},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"170","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"琳兹","text":"呃，那个好像是违反规定的吧......慢、慢点跑，我手臂要被你拽脱臼啦！","id":349,"figure":["avg_348_ceylon_1",1]},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"3","vibrato":"5","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":350},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"1","id":351},{"type":"dialog","id":352},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":353},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":354},{"type":"character","id":355},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":356},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","id":357,"musicid":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/23/Avg_bg_bg_offce.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":358},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":359},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":360},{"type":"character","name":"char_340_shwaz_2#2","fadetime":"0.5","id":361},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑","text":"老爷，小姐来信了。","id":363,"figure":["char_340_shwaz_2",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_024","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔曼","text":"嗯？你都要动身去接她回来了，这封信来得可真够晚的。","id":365,"figure":"avg_npc_024"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫尔曼","text":"我猜，那丫头一如既往地没在信里提到我。","id":366,"figure":"avg_npc_024"},{"type":"character","name":"char_340_shwaz_2","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑","text":"......","id":368,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2"},{"type":"character","id":369},{"type":"text","text":"黑的视线下意识地又一次扫过她已经记住内容的信件。","id":370},{"type":"dialog","id":371},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":372},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“......入冬之后的图书馆里似乎有一种靠源石技艺维持的暖炉，坐在里面读书非常惬意。我这个学期的借阅书单已经很长很长了。”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"middle","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":373},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“......随着和同学熟悉起来，我也得到了很多帮助。以前我寻求治疗矿石病的方法时，并没有想得太深入，但现在这些困惑已经化解了。”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":374},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“是的，我现在知道要如何破解矿石病的奥秘了。相信我，我很快就要找到它啦。”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":375},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“......随信附上一张贺卡，帮我转交给父亲吧。”","x":"300","y":"350","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":376},{"type":"subtitle","id":377},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":378},{"type":"text","text":"取出这沓信纸之后的信封是空的，国际信使的发信邮戳证明这封信在落款之后三天才寄出。","id":379},{"type":"character","name":"char_340_shwaz_2#1","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑","text":"（小姐一定又被什么东西迷住，把信的事情全忘记了吧。）","id":381,"figure":["char_340_shwaz_2",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_340_shwaz_2#5","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑","text":"不，老爷。小姐在信里特地祝您圣诞快乐，她很期待圣诞夜的餐桌。","id":383,"figure":["char_340_shwaz_2",4]},{"type":"dialog","id":384},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":385},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":386},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":387},{"type":"character","id":388},{"type":"image","fadetime":"2","id":389}],"characters":["商店广播","锡兰","琳兹","店员","黑","赫尔曼"]}